@2017 = ~This is a legendary weapon of heroic proportions, which is found mainly in the northern barbarian tribes. Master after master has swung this blade against countless enemies, and the blood that was spilled with this sword could fill a small sea. If the history is taken on faith, such a blade could not have been forged, and every owner seems to assign its origin to the myth, in which he currently believes. Probably the grandest origin story is that of a great chieftain, who sailed to the cliffs, which allegedly border the world. There he reached into emptiness and his will power shaped the blade out of nowhere. Whatever the truth may be: In the right hands, it is a fearsome weapon.

